{
  "text": "Platelet-rich plasma (PRP) and platelet-poor plasma were prepared from 3 healthy donors as described by Rasmussen et al [CITATION_1] . Bacterial concentration was set as described [CITATION_2] , and platelet aggregation was determined by aggregometry as described by Rasmussen et al [CITATION_3] . Soluble collagen was used as positive control.",
